The cut and paste the database settings code from 
\b settings.php
\b0  and put it where indicated in the comments in 
\b settings.local.php
\b0 .  Make sure that these database connection settings (the code shown above) does not remain in settings.php otherwise it will break the development site at pantheon.io. \
